caption: Very enthusiastic people. In the beginning it was a little bit difficult to find the place, but we were welcomed. Apparently they spoke Spanish but we don't speak it. After we said this, they brought us someone who translated to English which was very nice. We needed to leave earlier and that was no problem.
The atmosphere there is generous!

This church is a place of peace where we feel the presence of the Lord. The pastor couple Marco and Ella have in-depth and touching biblical teachings. In addition, this community is very fraternal and caring, we feel at home. A big thank you to the praise group who thrills us every Sunday and who, thanks to their talents, help us enter the presence of God.

I arrived in Paris in 2014, and I arrived at Rhema International, a wonderful Christian church, they welcomed me, with great love, very nice people, I recommend it because it is a place that preaches the word of God without adding or subtracting anything from it. and there are quite a few young people with whom to share experiences that we have and have had with God. I recommend it!!!!!
